00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:47.560
Sampai jumpa, Savi.

00:02:47.880 --> 00:02:49.400
Sampai jumpa, Dokter.

00:02:50.080 --> 00:02:51.200
Ayo pergi.

00:02:55.400 --> 00:02:58.600
Savi, cukup game.
